1. input number of test cases

2. for each test case:

    2.1. input the basic salary

    2.2. calculate the hra and da for each conditions

    if(bs < 1500):

        hra = float(bs * 0.1)

        da = float(bs * 0.9)

        2.2.1. print the result for each condition

        print(float(bs) + hra + da)

    if(bs >= 1500):

        hra = 500

        da = float(bs * 0.98)

        2.2.2. print the result for each condition

        print(float(bs) + float(hra) + da)

